OL,4,G1400FMurder She Wrote
OL,5,     GWhen a tennis star is killed by a
OL,6,     Gbomb planted in his girlfriend's
OL,7,     Gcar, all the evidence points
OL,8,     Gtowards the girlfriend and her
OL,9,     Gdead sister.
OL,10,G1500FMurder She Wrote
OL,11,     GA man is murdered in the midst of
OL,12,     GNew Orleans' Mardi Gras
OL,13,     Gcelebrations, and Jessica's
OL,14,     Gcousin is the chief suspect.
OL,15,G1600FMurder She Wrote
OL,16,     GAfter Jessica visits an old
OL,17,     Gfriend, a valuable painting is
OL,18,     Gstolen, but then her host is
OL,19,     Garrested following his daughter's
OL,20,     Gmurder.
