OL,4,G2000FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,5,     GThe tide of war turns against the
OL,6,     GAxis powers as the Allied forces
OL,7,     Gpush into the French Riviera.
OL,8,G2030FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,9,     GFollowing the D-Day invasions at
OL,10,     GNormandy, Allied forces joined
OL,11,     GFrench Resistance fighters.
OL,12,G2100FWWII Battles in Colour
OL,13,     GGripping stories brought to life
OL,14,     Gin never-before-seen colourised
OL,15,     Gbattle footage. It took only six
OL,16,     Gweeks for the Nazi army to
OL,17,     Gconquer France in the
OL,18,     Gextraordinary Blitzkrieg campaign.
