OL,4,G2200FWWII Battles in Colour
OL,5,     GOn June 22, 1941, Germany
OL,6,     Glaunched Operation Barbarossa, a
OL,7,     Gsavage and merciless attack on
OL,8,     Gthe Soviet Union, designed to
OL,9,     Gobliterate the Red Army and
OL,10,     Gmassacre its population.
OL,11,G2255FWWII Battles in Colour
